---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Contact">
  <section class="hero" style="padding-top: 80px; padding-bottom: 24px;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Contact</h1>
      <p>Want to add an agent, report a bug, talk business, or just say hi — drop us an email.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 640px;">
      <div class="contact-simple">
        <div class="contact-label">Email</div>
        <a class="contact-mail" href="mailto:andynaonao@gmail.com">andynaonao@gmail.com</a>
        <p class="contact-hint">Usually a reply within 48 hours. Add <code>[urgent]</code> to the subject line for faster turnaround.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose" style="margin-top: 48px;">
        <h2>When to reach out</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Missing an agent?</strong> Send us the homepage / GitHub link; once reviewed, it usually goes live within 1–2 business days.</li>
          <li><strong>Spotted stale info</strong> (star count, pricing, status, etc.)? Point it out and we'll verify and update.</li>
          <li><strong>Business / partnership</strong> (brand collaboration, content syndication, API data partnerships).</li>
          <li><strong>Found a bug on the site itself</strong> (not a problem with any listed agent).</li>
          <li><strong>Have something to say</strong> — any thoughts, suggestions, or honest criticism about the AI agent space are welcome.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Submission checklist (new agent)</h2>
        <p>To help us process things quickly, please include the following in your email:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Agent name + a one-line positioning</li>
          <li>Homepage / GitHub link</li>
          <li>License type (open source / commercial / freemium)</li>
          <li>One sentence on why it deserves a spot</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          The more complete the information, the faster the review. A solid submission is usually
          acknowledged within 1–3 business days, and you'll get an email once it's published.
        </p>

        <h2>What we usually don't reply to</h2>
        <p>To keep the inbox usable for everyone, we typically don't respond to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>SEO link exchanges / bulk backlink requests</li>
          <li>Unsolicited "exclusive interview" or guest invitations</li>
          <li>Promotions unrelated to the AI agent topic</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If that sounds like your request, apologies in advance — and thanks for understanding.</p>

        <h2>Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Your email is used only for this conversation. We will not add you to any mailing list or
          share it with third parties. To delete our previous correspondence, simply reply with
          "please delete my email." Full details are in the
          <a href="/privacy">privacy policy</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="verdict-box" style="margin-top: 24px;">
          <div class="label">Response time</div>
          <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text);">
            Weekdays &lt; 24h · Weekends / holidays 24–48h · Add <code>[urgent]</code> to halve it
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
